reviewText: I've watched the entire Gangland series.  The final season returned to form after Season 6.  I'd recommend it and its worth it.
I love these gangland series and wish they would continue,it is well put together and worth watching over & over.
Awesome. Just as I expected but even better! Works great on my computer and everything. Has tons of episodes to last awhile.

I was a latecomer to the Gangland Series and frankly, it's more than a bit scary to know certain types of people (aka gang members) are running around out in the world. Nevertheless, there are plenty of redeeming moments and people who have turned their lives around in this series.

I missed the special 75th episode with hosts Ice-T and Snoop Dogg and look forward to watching it on this final DVD collection. Obviously not for the young kids, but I would recommend it to families with teens; maybe finding out what really goes on in some of these gangs will keep them on the straight and narrow!

Well-done series, History!
